Subject: FEATURE: add support for random choice of transitions
Date: Thu, 20 May 2010 11:22:43 -0600
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

When a place has multiple transitions in its postset with true  
enabling conditions, randomly select one transition to fire.

Example:

process(place)
variable z:integer;
begin
	if (place = 0)
		z:=rand(2);
		if (z=1) then
			fire t1
		else
			fire t2


